{
  "stem": "7093.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I used to sit and listen to-- same like I listen to music.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I listened to French language, so that I-- I learned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And also, I had the most brilliant French teacher at school, who later on was with me in camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she didn't die, but I-- she died and I visited her then again before she died in our hometown.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she was the most brilliant teacher that ever existed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she got everybody to speak French very, very soon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because she-- we adored her to such an extent that nobody would have come to the lesson unprepared.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, her name was Magda Szemzo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, as I say, we all adored her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we-- so I spoke French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I spoke-- I learned English from my mother, who taught me quite-- from quite early on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's why I still have a German accent and not a Hungarian accent, which normally I would have.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then I-- so I worked with children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that year, that was '41 to '42, 1941 to 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And during that year, I also did a sewing course, a six-week sewing course and a one-week cooking course where I learned to do one cake on a special machine, which was the most useless course.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anyway, becoming a millinery was also not very useful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "First of all, I always hated the needle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And secondly, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I really didn't-- I found it-- that it wasn't for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I wanted to work with children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Now, I wanted to go to a training college.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But by that time, we couldn't go to a training college.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "A state training college wouldn't accept us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But in Budapest, the-- the community of [?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
